443
00:28:54,799 --> 00:28:55,970
Bagaimana bisa aku membiarkannya pergi?

444
00:29:01,410 --> 00:29:04,170
Kamu pasti sudah bertemu dengan banyak orang.

445
00:29:05,539 --> 00:29:06,539
Apa maksudmu?

446
00:29:06,539 --> 00:29:07,910
